{"tid":1647311,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"喂喂你地仲記唔記得由邊段片開始subscribe 大J呀？","createTime":"2019-10-11T16:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:43:05.000Z","uid":240448,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7e6252c606e49370b7b79fb6cc38290532bab482","tid":1647311,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"我講左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係由佢去重慶大廈過一晚夜，開始追佢既片。<br />\n<img src=\"https://youtu.be/tKeM6kmy3kE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtKeM6kmy3kE&h=a888a24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真心正 唔多youtuber 做到呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢都有幾多去香港探索既片<br />\n<br />\n個人認為佢既片比較多元化，會出去探險呀介紹下地方（郊外），唔駛下下駛好多錢打卡個種地方，出去食下野又拍下，分享生活所事 唔係千編一律咁。<br />\n<br />\n我知有堆人好耐之前可能唔係好like佢 <br />\n我之前無追開邊個 <br />\n但真心佢係一位成功既KOL <br />\n<br />\n分享下你地由邊段片開始關注佢丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 不是打手 真心respect"},{"pid":"c08f2b9db68e1ea890ec2b89f8aa6272d2339098","tid":1647311,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:42:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tKeM6kmy3kE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtKeM6kmy3kE&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=7027287a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tKeM6kmy3kE</a><br />\n<br />\n補一補"},{"pid":"ca2600bf8759791ffb87a8c7fe3747ef8f3d9caf","tid":1647311,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"由屯公條片subscribe"},{"pid":"bcc222a75dfd24d47dbaff96fff663c29b1d5f7f","tid":1647311,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"上年十月左右"},{"pid":"0e4421ecf537b6e1084f5aecfa852b2083d43318","tid":1647311,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪